dashboard.definition:
{
  "visualizations": {
    "viz_bg_header": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#0F2027",
        "strokeColor": "#00B4D8",
        "strokeWidth": 2
      }
    },
    "viz_header": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "# 📚 Panduan Lengkap Gemini SOC Assistant V2.1 (Studio Edition)\n**Tingkatkan kapabilitas analis keamanan Anda dengan asisten AI yang terintegrasi secara *native* di dalam Splunk.**\n\nAplikasi ini dirancang untuk membaca log secara pintar, memetakan ancaman ke framework MITRE ATT&CK, dan kini sepenuhnya mengadopsi arsitektur **Splunk Dashboard Studio**.",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent"
      }
    },
    "viz_bg_chat": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#1A2E3A",
        "strokeColor": "transparent",
        "strokeWidth": 0
      }
    },
    "viz_chat": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "### 💬 1. Gemini Studio Chat Assistant\nBerhenti menulis query SPL (Search Processing Language) yang rumit hanya untuk menganalisis payload. Gunakan menu **Gemini Chat Assistant**.\n\n- **Paste Log Mentah:** Anda dapat mem-paste log Windows Event, akses web, atau JSON mentah.\n- **Pilih Persona:** Sesuaikan output AI dengan audiens Anda (contoh: *Threat Hunter* untuk teknis, *Executive* untuk manajerial).\n- **Klik Analisis:** AI akan memproses log Anda tanpa noise/basa-basi dan langsung menampilkan temuan kritis.",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent"
      }
    },
    "viz_bg_generator": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#1A252F",
        "strokeColor": "transparent",
        "strokeWidth": 0
      }
    },
    "viz_generator": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "### 💡 2. AI Dashboard Studio Generator\nKesulitan mendesain Dashboard Studio yang rumit? Biarkan AI yang bekerja untuk Anda.\n\n- Navigasi ke menu **Dashboard Generator**.\n- Jelaskan apa yang Anda inginkan (contoh: *\"Buatkan dashboard pemantauan firewall dengan layout absolute, warna gelap, 2 grafik pie, dan 1 timechart\"*).\n- AI akan menghasilkan **kode JSON murni** yang bisa Anda langsung *copy-paste* ke *Source Editor* di Splunk.",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent"
      }
    },
    "viz_bg_spl": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#1E3745",
        "strokeColor": "transparent",
        "strokeWidth": 0
      }
    },
    "viz_spl": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "### ⚡ 3. Penggunaan Langsung via SPL\nJika Anda sedang berada di mode Search, Anda tetap dapat memanggil command `| geminianalyze` di ujung query Anda.\n\n**Analisis Per Baris Log (Single Mode):**\n```spl\nindex=wineventlog EventCode=4625 \n| head 10 \n| geminianalyze prompt=\"Identifikasi pola brute force.\"\n```\n**Analisis Rangkuman (Batch Mode):**\n```spl\nindex=firewall action=blocked \n| head 100 \n| geminianalyze prompt=\"Buat ringkasan serangan.\" batch=true role=\"threat_hunter\"\n```",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent"
      }
    },
    "viz_bg_setup": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#0D1B22",
        "strokeColor": "#06D6A0",
        "strokeWidth": 2
      }
    },
    "viz_setup": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "### ⚙️ 4. Konfigurasi Role & API Key\nJangan lupa untuk menyetel API Key Anda di halaman **Setup Page**.\nAnda juga dapat mengelola dan membuat **Role Kustom** baru di sana. Misalnya, role khusus analisis forensik dengan bahasa yang disesuaikan untuk tim Anda. Sistem baru kami memastikan API Key Anda direplikasi dengan aman bahkan di dalam arsitektur **Search Head Cluster**.",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent"
      }
    }
  },
  "layout": {
    "type": "absolute",
    "options": {
      "display": "auto",
      "backgroundColor": "#070E14"
    },
    "structure": [
      {
        "item": "viz_bg_header",
        "type": "block",
        "position": {"x": 20, "y": 20, "w": 1160, "h": 140}
      },
      {
        "item": "viz_header",
        "type": "block",
        "position": {"x": 40, "y": 30, "w": 1120, "h": 120}
      },
      {
        "item": "viz_bg_chat",
        "type": "block",
        "position": {"x": 20, "y": 180, "w": 570, "h": 220}
      },
      {
        "item": "viz_chat",
        "type": "block",
        "position": {"x": 40, "y": 190, "w": 530, "h": 200}
      },
      {
        "item": "viz_bg_generator",
        "type": "block",
        "position": {"x": 610, "y": 180, "w": 570, "h": 220}
      },
      {
        "item": "viz_generator",
        "type": "block",
        "position": {"x": 630, "y": 190, "w": 530, "h": 200}
      },
      {
        "item": "viz_bg_spl",
        "type": "block",
        "position": {"x": 20, "y": 420, "w": 1160, "h": 220}
      },
      {
        "item": "viz_spl",
        "type": "block",
        "position": {"x": 40, "y": 430, "w": 1120, "h": 200}
      },
      {
        "item": "viz_bg_setup",
        "type": "block",
        "position": {"x": 20, "y": 660, "w": 1160, "h": 140}
      },
      {
        "item": "viz_setup",
        "type": "block",
        "position": {"x": 40, "y": 670, "w": 1120, "h": 120}
      }
    ]
  }
}
